safetyTips: Drivers equipped with PPE and providing contact-free deliveries.
name: High Quality Food London
description: We are a South London based supplier of fine food. We have been working with restaurants and caterers around the city for the last 5 years, providing small-batch, high-quality ingredients. We stock all essential cupboard items: pasta and rice, flours, cereal, nuts, pulses, oil and condiments as well as fresh meat and fish, fruit & vegetables. We offer 2 days delivery and our drivers are equipped to deliver to those isolating. Delivery is free above Â£80.
